sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant DevKit
    participant Agent
    participant Repo
    participant System

    User->>DevKit: Intent / Goal
    DevKit->>Agent: Hydrate Context
    Repo->>Agent: Provide Context
    Agent->>DevKit: Normalized Workflow
    DevKit->>Agent: Execute Step
    Agent->>DevKit: Feedback / Result
    DevKit->>System: Execution
    System-->>DevKit: Drift Detected?
    DevKit-->>User: Done
    